By: Sri Ramakrishna
---
If you commit a sin, you must bear its fruit. But one who has attained
perfection, realized God, cannot commit sin. An expert singer cannot sing
a false note. A man with a trained voice sings the notes correctly： sâ,
re, gâ, mâ, pâ, dhâ, ni.
